      <h2>TurboJS tips</h2>
      <p><strong>Put your Javascripts in the &lt;head> element.</strong></p>
      <p>TurboJS is a brand-new javascript library developed in collaboration with <a href="http://twitter.com/maccaw">Alex MacCaw</a>. TurboJS is a unique new engine, designed to serve all your site's pages in the background - making your site super, duper, extra fast.</p>
    </article>

